{"talk":{"id":5498,"name":"Gautam Bhan: A bold plan to house 100 million people","description":"Mumbai, Delhi, Chennai, Kolkata -- all the major cities across India have one great thing in common: they welcome people arriving in search of work. But what lies at the other end of such openness and acceptance? Sadly, a shortage of housing for an estimated 100 million people, many of whom end up living in informal settlements. Gautam Bhan, a human settlement expert and researcher, is boldly reimagining a solution to this problem. He shares a new vision of urban India where everyone has a safe, sturdy home. (In Hindi with English subtitles)","slug":"gautam_bhan_a_bold_plan_to_house_100_million_people","recorded_at":"2017-12-10 00:00:00","published_at":"2017-12-11 15:00:51","updated_at":"2020-04-18 00:42:37","viewed_count":460330,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":472,"name":"TED Talks India"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/29ebdc61347c79cf13f8ad58c6e57dd18f7d0b5c_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/29ebdc61347c79cf13f8ad58c6e57dd18f7d0b5c_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/29ebdc61347c79cf13f8ad58c6e57dd18f7d0b5c_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/29ebdc61347c79cf13f8ad58c6e57dd18f7d0b5c_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/1d79b88bd495d5e8496790e0b000d2588be2c8f0_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/GautamBhan_2017I-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":4759171,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/GautamBhan_2017I-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":13135432,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/GautamBhan_2017I-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf7